Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.83,0:01:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二十六唱 天空和未来之颂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.94,0:02:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.36,0:02:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.04,0:02:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾居然被同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.56,0:02:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是看那表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.19,0:02:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是平常的那个她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.92,0:02:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们绝对无法对蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯大人下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.13,0:02:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定要了结一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.25,0:02:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么如此卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.01,0:02:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.18,0:02:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.11,0:02:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷 龙威 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.22,0:02:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只有封住蕾的武器了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不伤害蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.51,0:02:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只毁掉武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.83,0:02:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.46,0:03:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和拟煌珠相比简直有如天壤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.67,0:03:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量像是源源不断地涌出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不要再做垂死挣扎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.33,0:03:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七煌宝树在我们手中的现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.04,0:03:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们已没有赢的可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气干掉他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被你们干掉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“和我在一起”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会甘心被你们干掉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵抗是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.91,0:04:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.07,0:04:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.63,0:04:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.13,0:04:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们煌珠将终止你们守护者所缔造的愚蠢的历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.11,0:05:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了创造一个不再纷争的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是不再纷争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不会打算和我们守护者共存的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.05,0:05:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 你们只要不反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.30,0:05:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是可以确保让你们作为我们的道具生存的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想争战的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.74,0:05:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外别无他法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.16,0:05:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据古籍记载
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.95,0:05:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在久远的太古时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.71,0:05:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个煌珠乐园尚在大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.50,0:05:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煌珠与守护者共存着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里每个人都哼着歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.58,0:05:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以语言的灵力引导各种事情向好的方面发展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.58,0:05:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.94,0:05:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行吗 吉露露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.44,0:05:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.37,0:05:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时守护者们忘记歌颂而相互纷争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.28,0:05:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始把煌珠作为战斗的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.41,0:05:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.47,0:05:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此充斥着世界的波动开始紊乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煌珠乐园脱离开大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.20,0:06:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浮上了天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.64,0:06:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被守护者夺走了七煌宝树的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.87,0:06:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尊奉同伴中实力最强者为女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以其力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延续至今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.11,0:06:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也就到今天为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.18,0:06:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.68,0:06:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是得把蕾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把蕾封印起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.10,0:06:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外还有什么办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.63,0:06:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波涛汹涌为之征兆{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.26,0:06:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,澄净心灵静听{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求海神之救赎{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.06,0:06:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝向大海之原{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敞开双手{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇天之捧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.87,0:06:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.17,0:07:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.71,0:07:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.59,0:07:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的这一行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.16,0:07:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是不同种族无法共存的证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以你们所爱之人的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.46,0:07:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送你们下地狱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.20,0:07:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾也拼命地在抗争着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.17,0:08:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.76,0:08:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和守护者交往的话又会有纷争了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱逐守护者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.93,0:08:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创造煌珠的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.42,0:08:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真的就是幸福吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.96,0:08:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我不那么认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.90,0:08:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和守护者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.21,0:08:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人类相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同契之后感觉到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的煌珠也是有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.35,0:08:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是被守护者豢养的煌珠的幻想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.79,0:08:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是幻想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.57,0:08:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护者 煌珠想法一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能相互理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.63,0:08:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么会有守护翼的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.54,0:08:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想要保护我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.70,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们根本就不想被保护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.59,0:08:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们以“保护”这一迷人的名义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧妙地隔离我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.47,0:09:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这终究是因为视我们为危险的道具的缘故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想法一致？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在撒谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.93,0:09:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确或许是存在着错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.96,0:09:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.29,0:09:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是“也许有”就能解决的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.17,0:09:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因此劫持守护者 改造成拟煌珠就是对的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.64,0:09:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只不过是用同样的手法报复而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.45,0:09:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以别再干这种事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.03,0:09:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一再重演争战的不是你们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护者中并不都是那样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我们想和你们一起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.60,0:09:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管遭受多少教训都不会平息干戈的守护者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.32,0:09:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无未来可言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.42,0:09:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.24,0:09:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家如何如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煌珠如何如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些借口算什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.73,0:10:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为蕾是煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.45,0:10:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为蕾是蕾才喜欢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.19,0:10:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想一直在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.52,0:10:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样不行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.04,0:10:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗失颂词的守护者没有活着的价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.56,0:10:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷 躲开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.09,0:10:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天地{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.99,0:10:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.07,0:10:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你心中的所想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.05,0:11:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将它原原本本地传达出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.66,0:11:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.77,0:11:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你记得那语言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天地{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.89,0:11:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开化时所生{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既非人{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亦非地{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护国真言之灵{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.86,0:11:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣明所思{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.84,0:11:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣示力量{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.55,0:11:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,归于法则{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,归于道德{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻 归于一体{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷的颂词...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.81,0:11:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑海中...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.62,0:11:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生成{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.05,0:12:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美好之物{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生成{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻 归于一体{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生成{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟大之物{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生成{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝与我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.71,0:12:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不曾僭越{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合于文理{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所做之梦{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.22,0:12:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丝毫不差{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝与我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.05,0:12:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.71,0:12:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 到底...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.09,0:12:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这就是遗失的颂词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.88,0:12:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山清{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.72,0:12:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水秀{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人之笑颜{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.67,0:12:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无比珍贵{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.59,0:12:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美好{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.79,0:12:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天地{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.61,0:12:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相聚为乐{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.35,0:12:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千秋万代{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.20,0:13:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繁荣昌盛{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衷心祈愿{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.31,0:13:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫相忘{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.21,0:13:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若离别{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.02,0:13:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝与我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共同誓言{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.15,0:13:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到极限了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和卧鲁的契约...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.96,0:13:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卧鲁 看那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.90,0:13:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拟煌珠的人造核石正在消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.42,0:13:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.85,0:13:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的契约失效了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.24,0:13:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到了吗 酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.25,0:13:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.01,0:14:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗失的古代的颂词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.90,0:14:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然 居然在这时出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.63,0:14:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.86,0:14:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.21,0:14:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要讨厌守护者 人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.35,0:14:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家或许也会改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.81,0:14:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾芙丽·梅札兰斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.29,0:14:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧珐斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们输了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.17,0:14:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.58,0:14:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有失败感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.87,0:14:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听了酷的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.31,0:14:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.97,0:14:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.34,0:14:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.04,0:14:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想永远和你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.17,0:15:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷是酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.04,0:15:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 他们两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.14,0:15:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是珍贵无比的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.19,0:15:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我却将它斩断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.44,0:15:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 希丝卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.19,0:16:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.78,0:16:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各自又回到了自己的生活中努力了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.50,0:16:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理想的状况不知道能持续到什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.62,0:16:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但理想就是为了推动现实向理想靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.11,0:16:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.58,0:16:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也为了已牺牲的无数的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.13,0:16:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想再次重复悲伤的历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.86,0:17:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在守护翼总部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.55,0:17:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正缔结必不再战的协议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.68,0:17:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿今天的誓言在百年两百年之后仍铭刻在心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.33,0:17:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许理想实现是得在那么久远以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平的日子的的确确来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对此我毫不怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.13,0:17:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 大家的近况也说一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.04,0:17:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉撒蒂因为不用再战斗了松了一大口气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.48,0:17:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是听说最近被莉莉雅逼着穿女装很是头疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.05,0:17:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.55,0:17:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看 别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.99,0:17:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种衣服一点也不适合我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.04,0:17:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很配啊 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.77,0:17:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.12,0:18:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卧鲁克斯好像就职于守护翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.17,0:18:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了 吉露露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.26,0:18:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.77,0:18:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.68,0:18:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航向东北1时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.86,0:18:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏转45度方位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.45,0:18:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.11,0:18:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在仍想抓捕煌珠加以利用的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让本酷德·望·朱鲁爱特大爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狠狠地揍一顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.74,0:18:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.61,0:18:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.71,0:18:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.80,0:18:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.00,0:18:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.91,0:18:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.55,0:18:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.87,0:18:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气冲过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.05,0:18:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.59,0:19:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 好久不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.07,0:19:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为 为什么你会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.80,0:19:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想多增长些见识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.23,0:19:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是为了守护翼的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.57,0:19:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这些理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是想再次踏上旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.96,0:19:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你们一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好狡猾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.41,0:19:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好地方就你们两个人去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.51,0:19:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碍手碍脚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.61,0:19:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我和蕾的第一次出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.16,0:19:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种值得纪念的时刻相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.88,0:19:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们果然是有缘啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.55,0:19:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.89,0:19:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.14,0:19:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.68,0:19:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.74,0:19:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.86,0:19:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起突击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.91,0:19:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.14,0:19:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煌珠们已经保护起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.50,0:19:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.07,0:19:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.84,0:20:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年和少女的冒险暂且告一段落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.19,0:20:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但同时两人的故事又揭开了新的一页
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.65,0:20:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前方有什么在等待着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.99,0:20:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有困惑的时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.82,0:20:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有流泪的日子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.27,0:20:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.26,0:20:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信两人憧憬的未来是光明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.20,0:20:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那也是我们的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.84,0:20:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直飞到那颗星那里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.98,0:20:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能呼吸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.73,0:20:56.35,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,あの時君が見てた夢を追いかけて{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.73,0:20:56.35,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,追寻着你那时所见的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.84,0:21:09.82,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,僕等は今遠い道を步き始めてる{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.84,0:21:09.82,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们此刻开始远行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.88,0:21:24.38,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,君の目に映ってる世界の姿を{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.88,0:21:24.38,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,映现在你眼中的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.12,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,無口な指で分け合いたくて{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.12,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,以无言的手指与你分担
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.19,0:21:39.11,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,一人にはしないから{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.19,0:21:39.11,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你独自一人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.31,0:21:51.84,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,君の為に少しでも優しくなれたかな{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.31,0:21:51.84,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,为你尽量地温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.88,0:22:04.11,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,涙を微笑みに変える強さを僕は{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.88,0:22:04.11,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,把眼泪化作微笑的坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.75,0:22:09.65,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,まだ知らない{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.75,0:22:09.65,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我还未知
